,"image":{"sourceUrl":"https://content.kota.co.uk/app/uploads/2023/05/2-pixelartworks-2.jpg","mediaItemId":6391,"modified":"2023-05-17 11:44:48","imageFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.1494252873563218,"src":"/static/c45d2c1afead47f051ed8bb756f6be76/11042/2-pixelartworks-2.jpg","srcSet":"/static/c45d2c1afead47f051ed8bb756f6be76/a8669/2-pixelartworks-2.jpg 500w,\n/static/c45d2c1afead47f051ed8bb756f6be76/22a6f/2-pixelartworks-2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/c45d2c1afead47f051ed8bb756f6be76/11042/2-pixelartworks-2.jpg 2000w,\n/static/c45d2c1afead47f051ed8bb756f6be76/cf46b/2-pixelartworks-2.jpg 2500w","srcWebp":"/static/c45d2c1afead47f051ed8bb756f6be76/fbe34/2-pixelartworks-2.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/c45d2c1afead47f051ed8bb756f6be76/a27e8/2-pixelartworks-2.webp 500w,\n/static/c45d2c1afead47f051ed8bb756f6be76/c8563/2-pixelartworks-2.webp 1000w,\n/static/c45d2c1afead47f051ed8bb756f6be76/fbe34/2-pixelartworks-2.webp 2000w,\n/static/c45d2c1afead47f051ed8bb756f6be76/b1839/2-pixelartworks-2.webp 2500w","sizes":"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px"}}}}},{"__typename":"WordPress_Project_Workfields_MainContent_TextAndTitle","fieldGroupName":"Project_Workfields_MainContent_TextAndTitle","sectionNumber":"02.","text":"Our goal was to design a new website that not only positions PixelArtworks as a leader in immersive experiences, but also functions as a sales generation tool. We achieved this through our extensive research and design discovery phase, finding the sweet spot between modern user interface trends and a focused user experience.\r\n\r\nWe were lucky enough to have great brand guidelines and an extensive library of visual assets to use. We knew immediately that the white shards (which represent light) would be great for interactions within the new site. We animated them in After Effects and using Lottie we were able to create a bank of page, image and menu transitions. Doing these types of animations via code would usually take a developer days, but they can be done in just a few hours by a designer. They are also extremely well optimised for the web.","title":"Web Design"},{"__typename":"WordPress_Project_Workfields_MainContent_Spacer","fieldGroupName":"Project_Workfields_MainContent_Spacer","size":"large"},{"__typename":"WordPress_Project_Workfields_MainContent_Image","fieldGroupName":"Project_Workfields_MainContent_Image","dropShadow":"no","imageSize":"full_width","image":{"sourceUrl":"https://content.kota.co.uk/app/uploads/2023/05/3-pixelartworks-1.jpg","mediaItemId":6392,"modified":"2023-05-17 11:46:11","imageFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.492537313432836,"src":"/static/c632f92c075b53754a5331cff0a12a37/11042/3-pixelartworks-1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/c632f92c075b53754a5331cff0a12a37/a8669/3-pixelartworks-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/c632f92c075b53754a5331cff0a12a37/22a6f/3-pixelartworks-1.jpg 1000w,\n/static/c632f92c075b53754a5331cff0a12a37/11042/3-pixelartworks-1.jpg 2000w,\n/static/c632f92c075b53754a5331cff0a12a37/cf46b/3-pixelartworks-1.jpg 2500w","srcWebp":"/static/c632f92c075b53754a5331cff0a12a37/fbe34/3-pixelartworks-1.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/c632f92c075b53754a5331cff0a12a37/a27e8/3-pixelartworks-1.webp 500w,\n/static/c632f92c075b53754a5331cff0a12a37/c8563/3-pixelartworks-1.webp 1000w,\n/static/c632f92c075b53754a5331cff0a12a37/fbe34/3-pixelartworks-1.webp 2000w,\n/static/c632f92c075b53754a5331cff0a12a37/b1839/3-pixelartworks-1.webp 2500w","sizes":"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px"}}}}},{"__typename":"WordPress_Project_Workfields_MainContent_Video","fieldGroupName":"Project_Workfields_MainContent_Video","videoType":"file","videoSize":"full_width","embedLink":null,"loop":true,"fileLink":{"mediaItemUrl":"https://content.kota.co.uk/app/uploads/2023/05/web-animation-compressed6.mp4"},"posterImage":{"sourceUrl":"https://content.kota.co.uk/app/uploads/2023/05/video-cover.jpg","mediaItemId":6376,"modified":"2023-05-16 14:34:45","imageFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.7793594306049823,"src":"/static/f8c794eb007e3743f35a2bc476fcd69d/1a900/video-cover.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f8c794eb007e3743f35a2bc476fcd69d/a8669/video-cover.jpg 500w,\n/static/f8c794eb007e3743f35a2bc476fcd69d/22a6f/video-cover.jpg 1000w,\n/static/f8c794eb007e3743f35a2bc476fcd69d/1a900/video-cover.jpg 1920w","srcWebp":"/static/f8c794eb007e3743f35a2bc476fcd69d/e7136/video-cover.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/f8c794eb007e3743f35a2bc476fcd69d/a27e8/video-cover.webp 500w,\n/static/f8c794eb007e3743f35a2bc476fcd69d/c8563/video-cover.webp 1000w,\n/static/f8c794eb007e3743f35a2bc476fcd69d/e7136/video-cover.webp 1920w","sizes":"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"}}}}},{"__typename":"WordPress_Project_Workfields_MainContent_Spacer","fieldGroupName":"Project_Workfields_MainContent_Spacer","size":"large"},{"__typename":"WordPress_Project_Workfields_MainContent_TextAndTitle","fieldGroupName":"Project_Workfields_MainContent_TextAndTitle","sectionNumber":"03.","text":"One of the early decisions we had to make in development was whether to take the headless approach with the new site. This is usually done to speed up load times and to make page transitions smoother. However, the disadvantage is that it tends to cause unnecessary overheads. So instead, we opted for a nifty little library called Swup which, when combined with bespoke Lottie animations, gave us super smooth page transitions and quicker loading content.\r\n\r\nAs the website content features a lot of complex, parallax scrolling and GSAP animation, we complimented it with the Lenis smooth scrolling library. This means both Mac and PC users get the same, silky smooth scrolling experience. Everybody wins.\r\n\r\nOne of the client’s requests was to revamp the flat, 2D map on the old homepage, which displays their international offices. For a more visually interesting result, – we went 3D, creating a customised WebGL globe built in Three.js.\r\n\r\nVideo features extensively on the new site. To minimise the dreaded loading stutters, we used BunnyCDN to serve the assets and WPRocket to cache them for faster page loads.","title":"Development"},{"__typename":"WordPress_Project_Workfields_MainContent_Spacer","fieldGroupName":"Project_Workfields_MainContent_Spacer","size":"large"},{"__typename":"WordPress_Project_Workfields_MainContent_Image","fieldGroupName":"Project_Workfields_MainContent_Image","dropShadow":"no","imageSize":"full_width","image":{"sourceUrl":"https://content.kota.co.uk/app/uploads/2023/05/4-pixelartworks.jpg","mediaItemId":6388,"modified":"2023-05-17 11:35:07","imageFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.4204545454545454,"src":"/static/403b32fe82f618a875602d9954c2f4d7/11042/4-pixelartworks.jpg","srcSet":"/static/403b32fe82f618a875602d9954c2f4d7/a8669/4-pixelartworks.jpg 500w,\n/static/403b32fe82f618a875602d9954c2f4d7/22a6f/4-pixelartworks.jpg 1000w,\n/static/403b32fe82f618a875602d9954c2f4d7/11042/4-pixelartworks.jpg 2000w,\n/static/403b32fe82f618a875602d9954c2f4d7/cf46b/4-pixelartworks.jpg 2500w","srcWebp":"/static/403b32fe82f618a875602d9954c2f4d7/fbe34/4-pixelartworks.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/403b32fe82f618a875602d9954c2f4d7/a27e8/4-pixelartworks.webp 500w,\n/static/403b32fe82f618a875602d9954c2f4d7/c8563/4-pixelartworks.webp 1000w,\n/static/403b32fe82f618a875602d9954c2f4d7/fbe34/4-pixelartworks.webp 2000w,\n/static/403b32fe82f618a875602d9954c2f4d7/b1839/4-pixelartworks.webp 2500w","sizes":"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px"}}}}},{"__typename":"WordPress_Project_Workfields_MainContent_Spacer","fieldGroupName":"Project_Workfields_MainContent_Spacer","size":"large"},{"__typename":"WordPress_Project_Workfields_MainContent_BeforeAndAfter","fieldGroupName":"Project_Workfields_MainContent_BeforeAndAfter","beforeImage":{"sourceUrl":"https://content.kota.co.uk/app/uploads/2023/05/pixelartworks-before.jpg","mediaItemId":6364,"modified":"2023-05-16 13:34:20","imageFile":{"childImageSharp":{"s